														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1681181">
									

<p>See, this sort of stuff I can live with. It's an alternate universe thing, and it's intentionally silly to boot. It's when people write incredibly stupid and inaccurate stuff about Rome which is supposed to be taken seriously that I get angry.</p>
<p>Although the idea that humanity owns most of its troubles and strife to the Roman empire is irking in its utter inaccuracy.</p>

							</div>

								
